org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.parse

Class GenTezUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.parse.GenTezUtils

  • public class GenTezUtils
extends Object
    GenTezUtils is a collection of shared helper methods to produce TezWork. All the methods in this class should be static, but some aren't; this is to facilitate testing. Methods are made non-static on as needed basis.
